title: Nutri Ninja® Auto-iQ™ System - Testimonial 2
description:
Watch Rachel Beller - America's Get-Real Nutritionist - create this easy, fast and delicious Fiberized Start Up Super Juice using the Nutri Ninja® with Auto-iQ™ technology. See the pro extractor blades power through fresh and frozen ingredients with the press of a button. 

Fiberized Start Up Super Juice Recipe:

1 cup frozen blueberries
½ frozen peeled banana
½ cup spinach
1½ cups unsweetened vanilla almond milk
1 tablespoon protein powder
1 tablespoon white chia seeds
¾ teaspoon ground Ceylon cinnamon
